snippet.title: Panzer Paladin - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Hop in the Paladin power armor, seize melee weapons from the demonic invaders and give them a taste of their own medicine!
Available now: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/panzer-paladin-switch/
